    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The problem is that having a lot of MEV transactions with 0 gas price will confuse the gas price oracle. In 1.10.4 we fixed the gas price oracle to ignore 0 gas price transactions.\r\nYou can download and build the master branch as shown here: https://geth.ethereum.org/docs/install-and-build/installing-geth#build-go-ethereum-from-source-code",
